Please use the script kindly prodivded for learnign purposes here : https://github.com/simonprickett/bash-traffic-lights-pi/blob/master/trafficlights.sh
Just change in it : 

# Assign names to GPIO pin numbers for each light
RED=9
YELLOW=10
GREEN=11

to 

# Assign names to GPIO pin numbers for each light
BLUE=4
RED=17
GREEN=27
